title: Arista Switches: Fans
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/arista
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the fans of Arista Networks switches via the SNMP
 ENTITY-SENSOR-MIB. Sensors reporting their unit as RPM are treated as
 fans.

 Lower and upper levels for the fan speed can be configured via the rule
 "Fans". The sensor's own status is evaluated as well: status 1 is {OK},
 status 2 is {WARN}.

discovery:
 One service is created for each sensor reporting its unit as RPM.

item:
 The entity description of the fan, with a leading "Fan " prefix stripped.
